A referendum failed by a vote of 36 No's and 24 Yes's. To make this pie chart of this result, what is the lesser measure in degrees of angle $ACB$?

[asy]
import graph;
draw(Circle((0,0),20));
draw((0,0)--(0,20));
draw((0,0)--(12,-16));
label("$A$",(0,20),N);
label("$B$",(12,-16),SE);
label("$C$",(0,0),W);
label("YES",(10,13),S);
label("NO",(-10,13),S);
label("36",(-10,10),S);
label("24",(10,10),S);
[/asy]
